Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員用英語說話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣
